WEBVTT

01:17.360 --> 01:18.760 line:80%
That won't work, either.

01:19.480 --> 01:21.110 line:80%
Dear, why are you pulling me?

01:21.170 --> 01:22.500 line:80%
If a woman wanted to borrow you from me,

01:22.500 --> 01:23.780 line:80%
would you be okay with it?

01:23.780 --> 01:26.640 line:80%
Well, if she were gentle,
I guess I wouldn't mind.
